//   □ Rename fields to camelCase (add @map for DB name)
//   □ Add missing relations if FK not migrated
//   □ Convert String fields to enum if desired
//   □ Review DateTime fields map to correct Prisma types
//   □ Verify Boolean fields (from TINYINT(1)) are correct
